== 播出 ==
《異域天使》最初由[[日本|日本]][[東京電視台|東京電視台]]播放，從2004年4月5日至同年9月27日結束<ref name="TVT_lineup">{{cite web|url=http://www.c-direct.ne.jp/tvtokyo/eng/pg_lineup/pdf/2004_april.pdf |title=Program lineup |accessdate=2006-10-29 |format=PDF |publisher=[[東京電視台|東京電視台]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080229065609/http://www.c-direct.ne.jp/tvtokyo/eng/pg_lineup/pdf/2004_april.pdf |archivedate=2008-02-29 |language=en |date=2004年4月 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

即將播放結束時，它在北美和歐洲得到[[ADV_Films|ADV Films]]的授權<ref name="ADV_PR">{{cite web |url=http://www.advfilms.com/Home/AnimeNews/tabid/105/newsid467/6311/ADV-Films-Makes-Acquisition-Announcement-at-Anime-Weekend-Atlanta/Default.aspx |title=ADV Films makes acquisition announcement at Anime Weekend Atlanta: ''MADLAX'' licensed |accessdate=2006-10-29 |date=2004-09-28 |publisher=[[ADV_Films|ADV Films]] |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081120011745/http://www.advfilms.com/Home/AnimeNews/tabid/105/newsid467/6311/ADV-Films-Makes-Acquisition-Announcement-at-Anime-Weekend-Atlanta/Default.aspx |archivedate=2008-11-20 }}</ref>。ADV Films以前曾獲得《NOIR》的發行權，所以早已計劃好對其續篇進行授權<ref name="Ac_ann">{{cite web |url=http://anime.about.com/od/animenews/a/aa093004.htm |title=ADV Announces ''MADLAX'' |accessdate=2007-03-14 |last=Luther |first=Katherine |publisher=[[About.com|About.com]] |date=2004-10-02 |quote=合作創辦人[[Matt_Greenfield|Matt Greenfield]]說：'We've been waiting for this show ever since ''Noir'' ended,' |archive-date=2007-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071224154723/http://anime.about.com/od/animenews/a/aa093004.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。從2005年4月12日到2006年3月28日，美國以「MADLAX」為商標發售英文官方[[配音|配音]]版，總共包括7盤DVD。ADV亦於2007年7月17日發行完整收藏版<ref name="Mania_CC_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/madlax-complete-collection-thinpak_article_79417.html |title=''Madlax'' Complete Collection (Thinpack) review |publisher=Mania.com |accessdate=2008-09-22 |date=2007-11-29 |author=Coulter, Bryce |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030200522/http://www.mania.com/madlax-complete-collection-thinpak_article_79417.html |archivedate=2014-10-30 }}</ref>。《異域天使》成了ADV Films的導演和製作人利用[[點對點技術|點對點技術]][[BitTorrent_(协议)|BitTorrent]]對分配[[促銷|促銷]]材料技術進行試驗的第一部系列作品<ref name="BT-promo">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2005-07-14/adv-bittorrent-test |title=''ADV Bittorrent Test'' |accessdate=2006-10-29 |date=2005-07-14 |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]] |language=en |archive-date=2015-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226203607/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2005-07-14/adv-bittorrent-test |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

