== 相關媒體 ==
北美銷售的DVD收錄了僅限英語版的附加視頻，比如自我[[戲仿|戲仿]]視頻「和SSS的交談」（{{lang-en|''Conversations with SSS''}}）<ref name="DV_V1_rev" /><ref name="DV_V7_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol7.php |title=''Madlax'' DVD #7 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Hattaway, Mitchell |date=2006-04-20 |publisher=DVDVerdict.com |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061212144106/http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol7.php |archivedate=2006-12-12 }}</ref><ref name="Mania_V7_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/madlax-vol-7_article_78027.html |title=''Madlax'' DVD #7 review |accessdate=2008-09-22 |author=Beveridge, Chris |date=2006-04-13 |publisher=Mania.com |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415194001/http://www.mania.com/madlax-vol-7_article_78027.html |archivedate=2015-04-15 }}</ref>，以及關於瑪德拉絲尋找{{link-en|克里斯·巴頓|Chris Patton}}（潘妮莎的同事巴吉斯（{{lang|ja|バジス}}）的英文配音員和一位製造麻煩的花花公子（劇中））的[[彩蛋_(視覺)|彩蛋]]{{link-en|實寫|Self-parody}}短片<ref name="ANN_V67_rev">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/madlax/dvds-6-7 |title=''Madlax'' DVD #6 and #7 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Martin, Theron |date=2006-04-05 |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]] |language=en |archive-date=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117032350/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/madlax/dvds-6-7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>「傀儡劇場」（英文：''Sock Puppet Theater''）。

自2006年2月7日以來，《異域天使》在{{link-en|動畫網|Anime Network}}上播放（它和ADV Films一樣是[[A.D._Vision|A.D. Vision]]的子公司）。在4月4日，即最後一卷DVD推出後不久，播放就随之中止了。直到6月27日，只有前8集被重播。自從那以後，《異域天使》被數次重播<ref name="AN-air">動畫網2006年的節目編排：[http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-02-07 2月7日] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080623200138/http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-02-07 |date=2008-06-23 }}，[http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-06-27 6月27日]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060623194119/http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-06-27 |date=2006-06-23 }}，[http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-08-01 8月1日] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080623200148/http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-08-01 |date=2008-06-23 }} 和 [http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-11-07 11月7日]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061119201747/http://www.theanimenetwork.com/testsched_GEH.php?schedday=2006-11-07 |date=2006-11-19 }}，於2006年11月15日查閱．</ref>。

先前在其區域之内授權予「NOIR」的麥德曼娛樂公司（Madman Entertainment）獲得了在澳大利亞和新西蘭分銷「異域天使」的權利。麥德曼娛樂在2005年7月20日至2006年7月26日期間推出了《異域天使》DVD版（共7卷）<ref name="ME_off">{{cite web |url=http://www.madman.com.au/madlax/index2.html |title=''異域天使'' |publisher=[[麥德曼娛樂|麥德曼娛樂]] |accessdate=2008-01-21 |language=en |archive-date=2013-02-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EFJr0TAK?url=http://www.madman.com.au/madlax/index2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後於2007年4月4日推出了完全收藏版<ref name="ME_off" />。

=== 原聲音樂 ===
[[File:Madlax_OST_I_cover.jpg|thumb]]
[[Victor_Entertainment|Victor Entertainment]]於2004年7月21日<ref name="OST1">{{cite web|url=http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A016061/VICL-61319.html|title=''MADLAX'' O.S.T.|publisher=Victor Entertainment|accessdate=2008-07-06|language=ja|archive-date=2009-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090401141629/http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A016061/VICL-61319.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和9月22日<ref name="OST2">{{cite web|url=http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A016061/VICL-61320.html|title=''MADLAX'' O.S.T.2|publisher=Victor Entertainment|accessdate=2008-07-06|language=ja|archive-date=2009-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601093943/http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A016061/VICL-61320.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>推出了《異域天使》的兩張[[原聲音樂|原聲音樂]][[專輯|專輯]]「MADLAX O.S.T」和「MADLAX O.S.T.2」。另外[[FictionJunction|FictionJunction YUUKA]]於同年推出兩張[[單曲|單曲]]「{{lang|ja|瞳の欠片}}」<ref name="HnK">{{cite web|url=http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A018153/VICL-35627.html|title=''Hitomi no Kakera''|publisher=Victor Entertainment|accessdate=2008-07-06|language=ja|archive-date=2009-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829130715/http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A018153/VICL-35627.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和「inside your heart」<ref name="iyh">{{cite web|url=http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A018153/VICL-35646.html |title=''inside your heart'' |publisher=Victor Entertainment |accessdate=2008-07-06 |language=ja |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829130721/http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/-/Discography/A018153/VICL-35646.html |archivedate=2009-08-29 }}</ref>。每張單曲包含片頭、片尾主題曲和一首插入曲，還有它們各自的[[卡拉OK|卡拉OK]]版。

=== 原畫集 ===
《MADLAX the Bible》（ISBN 4-89425-375-5）是{{link-ja|Hobby Japan|ホビージャパン}}於2005年5月21日在日本出版的一本95頁的原畫集<ref name="HLJ_book">{{cite web|url=http://www.hlj.com/product/HBJ25375|title=''MADLAX the Bible''|publisher=HobbyLink Japan|accessdate=2008-07-07|archive-date=2015-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928002241/http://www.hlj.com/product/HBJ25375|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了該系列的[[插畫|插畫]]和原畫之外，它包含了對作者和聲優的採訪，以及關於這部作品廣泛的額外日文信息<ref name="MtB">{{cite web|url=http://www.hobbyjapan.co.jp/madlax/ |title=''Madlax the Bible'' |accessdate=2006-10-29 |publisher=Hobby Japan |language=ja |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060805182932/http://www.hobbyjapan.co.jp/madlax/ |archivedate=2006-08-05 }}</ref>。此書並未在日本以外出版。由於"Bible"一詞是從[[古希臘語|古希臘語]]{{lang|grc|"τὰ βιβλία τὰ ἅγια"}}（意思是神聖之書）衍生出來，這本原畫集的標題很有可能暗示了在整個系列的劇情中出現並佔有重要地位的三本繪本（聖典）。

=== 週邊商品 ===
一個名為「帶槍的瑪德拉絲」（Madlax with Guns）的[[樹脂|樹脂]][[比例模型|比例模型]]已被製造出來，這一[[手辦|人物模型]]展現了一位雙手持[[SIG_P210手槍|SIG P210]]的瑪德拉絲<ref name="MwG">{{cite web |url=http://www.homemedia4u.com/catalog/product_info.php?products_id=1716 |title=''Madlax with Guns'' |accessdate=2007-02-11 |publisher=HomeMedia4U.com |date=2006-08-19 |language=en |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924173728/http://www.homemedia4u.com/catalog/product_info.php?products_id=1716 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。還有一個名為「瑪德拉絲」的Polystone人物模型也於2007年8月在日本推出<ref name="HLJ_figure">{{cite web |url=http://www.hlj.com/product/CADGK-04 |title=''Madlax'' |accessdate=2007-12-05 |publisher=HobbyLink Japan |archive-date=2015-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927191304/http://www.hlj.com/product/CADGK-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在日本，一件印有瑪德拉絲標誌的[[T恤|T恤]]則作為第一卷DVD限定版的連帶商品<ref name="AmJp_V1">{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.co.jp/Madlax/dp/B0002AP27O/ |title=''Madlax'' DVD #1 with series box and T-shirt |accessdate=2007-02-11 |publisher=[[Amazon.co.jp|Amazon.co.jp]] |date=2004-07-21 |language=ja |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929111855/http://www.amazon.co.jp/Madlax/dp/B0002AP27O/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。並且OST專輯的初回限定盤附送了標識語[[鼠標墊|鼠標墊]]。<ref name="CDJ_OST1">{{cite web |url=http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=VICL-61319 |title=''Madlax OST I'' |accessdate=2007-02-20 |publisher=CDJapan.co.jp |date=2004-07-21 |language=en |archive-date=2013-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005015513/http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=VICL-61319 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{clear}}

== 評價 ==
《異域天使》經常被批評與《[[NOIR|NOIR]]》相似或引用《NOIR》的設定，比如故事劇情、兩位主角皆為女性、主角的外觀相似性和音樂旋律等<ref name="ANN_V1_rev">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/madlax/dvd-1 |title=''Madlax'' DVD #1 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Martin, Theron |date=2005-05-06 |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]] |language=en |archive-date=2016-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204153429/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/madlax/dvd-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亦有評論稱讚指《異域天使》的故事比《NOIR》更具備整體性和連貫性，原因為首要劇情和次要劇情在全劇中有不可分割和良好的連貫<ref name="Mania_V7_rev" /><ref name="DV_V2_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol2.php |title=''Madlax'' DVD #2 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Hattaway, Mitchell |date=2005-09-01 |publisher=DVDVerdict.com |quote=...every new twist only strengthens the plot. Yes, the story is quite complex, but it doesn't appear to be complex just for the sake of being complex. The plot is a big puzzle, but I have a feeling all of the pieces will eventually fall into place. |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060519035736/http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol2.php |archivedate=2006-05-19 }}</ref>。

不少評論指作品前期劇情描述緩慢，感覺劇情乏味<ref name="AJ_V1_rev" />。有人則認為前期的長描述對於意想不到的結局來說是不錯的表現方式，因為對劇情的描述不同於其他作品，而使作品能獨樹一格<ref name="DVDTalk_rev" /><ref name="Mania_V7_rev" /><ref name="ANN_V67_rev" /><ref name="DV_V6_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol6.php |title=''Madlax'' DVD #6 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Hattaway, Mitchell |date=2006-02-07 |publisher=DVDVerdict.com |quote=Sure, at first glance ''Madlax'' appears to be nothing more than another run-of-the-mill girls-with-guns anime, but this series goes a long way to proving that the devil's in the details. Unless they really blow things at the end, this will go down as one terrific series. |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061212144053/http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol6.php |archivedate=2006-12-12 }}</ref>。有評論讚賞劇情從第一集起，每新一集都令人感覺越加精彩<ref name="Mania_V4_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/madlax-vol-4_article_78358.html |title=''Madlax'' DVD #4 review |accessdate=2008-09-22 |author=Morton, Bryan |date=2006-09-28 |publisher=Mania.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821150931/http://www.mania.com/madlax-vol-4_article_78358.html |archivedate=2014-08-21 }}</ref><ref name="DV_V3_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol3.php |title=''Madlax'' DVD #3 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Hattaway, Mitchell |date=2005-09-15 |publisher=DVDVerdict.com |quote=This series keeps getting better and better.  I keep waiting for ''Madlax'' to implode, but it somehow manages to keep on chugging along. |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061212144041/http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/madlaxvol3.php |archivedate=2006-12-12 }}</ref>。有評論則認為結局的[[存在主義|存在主義]]，是屬於[[虛假陳述|虛假性質]]的<ref name="DV_V7_rev" />。除此之外，也有人高度讚賞黑田的劇本，稱它為“BEE TRAIN的最佳文章”<ref name="EF_V7_rev">{{cite web |url=http://okazu.blogspot.com/2006/07/yuri-anime-madlax-volume-7.html |title=''Madlax'' DVD #7 review |accessdate=2007-10-25 |author=艾麗卡·弗里德曼 |date=2007-07-03 |quote=It's a magic with no roots in our world, so we have to take everything we're given at face value,.. [...] I still maintain that ''Madlax'' is the best writing that Bee Train has done. It has the mystery of the ''.hack'' series, without the endless meaningless chatter that goes nowhere, the yuri and violence of ''Noir'', the despair and love of ''Avenger'' and a story that resolves, unlike all of them. |language=en |archive-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5w4ADQs7n?url=http://okazu.blogspot.com/2006/07/yuri-anime-madlax-volume-7.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及覺得“角色使人非常同情”<ref name="Mania_V6_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/madlax-vol-6_article_77932.html |title=''Madlax'' DVD #6 review |accessdate=2008-09-22 |author=Beveridge, Chris |date=2006-01-26 |publisher=Mania.com |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325075015/http://www.mania.com/madlax-vol-6_article_77932.html |archivedate=2015-03-25 }}</ref>。部分評論則覺得個別男性角色如弗莱迪、卡洛沙和巴頓上校，與《NOIR》中類似暴風突擊隊的Soldats組織成員很截然不同<ref name="AJ_V1_rev" />。部分評論則認為相對於平凡的男性角色，女性角色的設計過於詳細<ref name="ANN_V67_rev" />。

《異域天使》在[[動畫|動畫]]上的高質量得到了公眾的普遍承認<ref name="Mania_V7_rev" /><ref name="ANN_V1_rev" />。負評方面，有關電腦[[黑客|黑客]]的劇情被人批評不夠現實<ref name="Mania_V3_rev" />。就[[原聲音樂|原聲音樂]]來說，《異域天使》在創新上還達不到像《NOIR》那樣<ref name="AA_OST1_rev">{{cite web|url=http://www.activeanime.com/pn/index.php?name=News&file=article&sid=2343 |title=''Madlax OST I'' review |accessdate=2007-07-27 |author=Salandanan, Rommel |date=2005-11-14 |publisher=ActiveAnime.com |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927193022/http://www.activeanime.com/pn/index.php?name=News&file=article&sid=2343 |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>。評論家們認為它的原聲音樂是《NOIR》和《[[.hack|.hack//Sign]]》風格的混合體<ref name="ANN_V2_rev">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/madlax/dvd-2 |title=''Madlax'' DVD #2 review |accessdate=2006-11-08 |author=Martin, Theron |date=2005-06-28 |publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |quote=The musical scoring, which sounds like a mix of ''Noir'' and ''.hack//SIGN'' |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422152234/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/madlax/dvd-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，評論員們承認它相對於同時期作品的優越性<ref name="AJ_V1_rev" /><ref name="ANN_V1_rev" />。ADV Films推出的英文翻譯版本由於忠實展現系列的原貌以及邀請資深配音員參與配音工作被稱讚<ref name="Mania_V4_rev" />。評論員們甚至認為一些英文配音（特別是{{link-en|麥克·克萊恩茲|Mike Kleinhenz}}的配音）比起日文原配和角色更為搭配<ref name="ANN_V67_rev" />。

《異域天使》起初的，特別是和《NOIR》最早的幾集相比<ref name="ANN_V1_rev" />的緩慢進度成了觀眾常常在故事進入「讓《異域天使》最終獲得一定程度上成功」的精彩階段前就放棄觀看該作品的最主要的原因<ref name="ANN_V1_rev" />。其他一些被人提出的關於導致本作人氣平平的原因包括：其他動畫自2001年以來因試圖效仿《NOIR》的成功之路而造成的市場飽和；人們意料之中的對重新製作《NOIR》所持的冷淡態度，經發現這種態度在《NOIR》的粉絲中是存在的<ref name="AJ_V1_rev" />。由於《異域天使》的動作場景過於夸大以至於一些人認為是荒謬的<ref name="THEM_rev">{{cite web |url=http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=817 |title=''Madlax'' (first two episodes) review |accessdate=2007-01-10 |author=Ross, Carlos |publisher=THEM Anime Reviews |quote=Usually, a show like this is saved by its dramatic themes and its action sequences. Noir was. Madlax is not... The "action" is so over-the-top as to cross the line between cool and stupid... Maybe future episodes will prove me wrong, but for now, ''Madlax'' is frustratingly mediocre and extremely difficult to find the motivation to continue. |language=en |archive-date=2016-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222161545/http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=817 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，還有它那種不合常規的風格，令《異域天使》不自然地跨越於愛好神秘[[科幻小說|科幻小說]]的人和那些喜歡《NOIR》那樣嚴格[[現實主義|現實主義]]的人之間<ref name="Mania_V6_rev" />。

